      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle exemplifies the pinnacle of preservation, maintained to an exacting standard that satisfies even the most discerning collector. Every surface, mechanical component, and aesthetic detail remains in a state of superlative refinement, mirroring its original delivery specifications. We invite you to experience a motorcar that transcends the typical pre-owned market, offering a rare opportunity to acquire excellence without compromise.",
