    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Honestly, I\u2019m going to miss this beauty so much! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s been pampered with regular detailing. If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
