    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you\u2014it is in incredible shape! Seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
