    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The dual-VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. Suspension remains tight with original geometry, and the limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction. No mechanical flaws, zero leaks, and a perfectly preserved chassis. This is a collector-quality driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist.",
